short_description: Interviews with Kubrick's colleagues and family members, including executive producer Jan Harlan, art director Les Tomkins, and Kubrick's daughter Katharina, who worked on location scouting for the film.

facts_and_links: {'Trivia': ['Michael Sheen\'s father, Meyrick Sheen has had a long career spanning over three decades as a lookalike thanks to his striking resemblance to the Hollywood legend. In an interview on \'This Morning\', Michael said: "A very long time ago when I was in drama school, during the late \'80s and early \'90s, people started coming up to my dad and said, \'You look exactly like Jack Nicholson.\' It was around the time the first \'Batman\' movies were coming out, the Tim Burton ones where Jack Nicholson played The Joker. That eventually led him to get an agent and to work all over the world as a Jack Nicholson lookalike ... My dad used to say, \'Even better than the real thing!\' I\'ve always said that what my dad lacks in specificity, makes up for him in commitment, so I think I\'ve taken after him in that respect."', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt32981763/trivia/?ref_=tt_dyk_trv']}
